TCP CONNECT : nmap -sT IP

CONFIGURE FIREWALL TO RETURN RESET : iptables -I INPUT -p tcp --dport <port> -j REJECT --reject-with tcp-reset

STEALTH SCANS : nmap -sS IP

UDP SCANS : nmap -sU IP

SCAN N MOST COMMON PORTS : nmap -sU --top-ports N IP


FOR FIREWALL EVASION : 

    NULL SCANS : nmap -sN IP

    FIN SCANS : nmap -sF IP

    XMAS SCANS : nmap -sX IP

PING SWEEP : nmap -sn IP_Range